te the listed buildings and conservation area of the Match Factory.<\\/p><p>Following a successful planning application on behalf of Brook Henderson Estates, the site was sold and the project was subsequently delivered by Aitch Group \\/ BLA Architects.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"300\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"30\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"75b1f7f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c47eec6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"carousel\":[{\"id\":154,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/sh-arms\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/08\\/project-3-1.jpg\"},{\"id\":155,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/sh-arms\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/08\\/project-3-2.jpg\"}],\"thumbnail_size\":\"full\",\"slides_to_show\":\"1\",\"navigation\":\"arrows\",\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\",\"caption_type\":\"caption\",\"caption_text_color\":\"#9D9D9D\",\"caption_typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"caption_typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":12,\"sizes\":[]},\"caption_typography_font_weight\":\"300\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-carousel\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
