(191, 1, '2020-08-05 13:52:16', '2020-08-05 13:52:16', '<h2>about</h2>\nFounded in 2018 by Muhammad Sagitha, an integrated architectural design practice based in Jakarta, Indonesia.\n\nArMS provides Architecture, Interior, Master Planning, and Furniture design at all levels and scales.\n\nArMS is an abbreviation of Architect Muhammad Sagitha, he was formerly a founding partner of SUB architects in 2009 and worked at WOHA in Singapore in 2006.\n\nCombining innovative thinking and efficient solution, through the process we discover a unique concept for each project without diminishing the emotions of its particular characteristics to make it alive\n\nWorks of architecture are kept on developing. Our vision is to make the design quality in Indonesia becomes better and Indonesian architecture to be internationally recognized\n<h2>the people</h2>\n<figure>\n					<img src=\"http://localhost/sh-arms/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro_ms.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<h3>Muhammad Sagitha</h3>\n<h4>Principal Architect</h4>\n<figure>\n					<img src=\"http://localhost/sh-arms/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro_agg.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<h3>Anggita Paramita</h3>\n<h4>Principal Interior</h4>\n<figure>\n					<img src=\"http://localhost/sh-arms/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro_adt.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<h3>Muhammad Bagus Aditya</h3>\n<h4>Senior Architectural Designer</h4>\n<figure>\n					<img src=\"http://localhost/sh-arms/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro_ang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<h3>Angga Nugraha</h3>\n<h4>Architectural Designer</h4>\n<figure>\n					<img src=\"http://localhost/sh-arms/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro_ard-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<h3>Ardi Kurniadi</h3>\n<h4>Architectural Designer</h4>\n<figure>\n					<img src=\"http://localhost/sh-arms/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro_and-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<h3>Andri Hadian</h3>\n<h4>Technical</h4>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-08-05 13:52:16', '2020-08-05 13:52:16